    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my absolute pride and joy! This car is honestly in stunning, showroom-ready shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since the day I brought it home. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, hand-washed every weekend, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come take a look or have any questions at all!",
      "price": 44500.0,
