    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to an exacting standard. The heart of this machine is the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine, displaying factory-spec compression across all faces. Its sequential twin-turbocharged system provides a linear power band with immediate spool-up, managed by a precise 5-speed short-throw gearbox. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, featuring the original lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension for telepathic handling. This example boasts a Torsen limited-slip differential and zero evidence of heat-cycle fatigue in the vacuum lines or harness. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector seeking peak apex-hunting performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
