    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and looks exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, thanks to a professional ceramic coating applied annually. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain supple with no visible bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record from day one, all performed by certified technicians using only OEM parts. Every electronic component, button, and switch functions perfectly. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. Included with the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and the original owner\u2019s manuals. If you are looking for the absolute best example on the market, this is it.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
